**Name of the game you would like to be added**
The FULL and complete name of the game

**Where we can find the game**
The URL (link) to where we can find the game

**Why we should add this game**
Give us a reason why this game should be added to NeonWave

**Is this game considered 18+ Material?**
18+ Material CAN be added to NeonWave, but has to be restricted. Some types of 18+ Material cannot be added to NeonWave

**A short description on what the game is about**
A short explination of what the game is about, what the aim is, etc.

**Anything else?**
Anything else you want to tell us?

*Your game will be reviewed by the Admins of NeonWave and should be accepted within 60 days at most.*
